name: Speed Wheat [Ludum Dare 52]
description:
Frost is coming, and you have to collect your harvest RIGHT NOW!!!!

Using only your mouse, click to completely flash your wheat into pieces off your 6 plots of land. You have to hurry, because the more efficient farmer gets more of the glory!!!

Web Build has a 5% chance of working for some reason. If it doesn't show up for you try downloading the build in the description
